{"tid":2123183,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"尖東持刀賊劫找換店職員 掠走180萬元逃去無蹤","createTime":"2020-07-24T12:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T12:51:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5ccb8562fadfc8864b8499d075fcbcbb3635c1fd","tid":2123183,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200724/G3GXPEUCTGJG4LYOTO2BZCZWGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200724%2FG3GXPEUCTGJG4LYOTO2BZCZWGA%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=97f9330b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200724%2FG3GXPEUCTGJG4LYOTO2BZCZWGA%2F&h=601fd5b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200724/G3GXPEUCTGJG4LYOTO2BZCZWGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n晚上7時許，尖東港晶中心一間找換店，有一男一女職員帶了一個裝有約180萬的背囊離開店舖，原因不明。兩名職員其後沿科學館道往紅磡火車站方向而行，當行至科學館道近行人天橋底時，突然被兩名持刀賊施襲，爭執間男職員背部受創。賊人搶走背囊後，隨即往加拿芬道跑走，女職員一度試圖追上，惟賊人最後登上一輛白色私家車逃去無蹤。"},{"pid":"9995daeb22775dd7edcdd73fed7808f60528acdb","tid":2123183,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗姐"},{"pid":"c0d05a08f2dfc91bd68f08f90c9a62e974058c3d","tid":2123183,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"354840b59b181b3fa9471f11f2cf2d8a37dde68f","tid":2123183,"uid":98242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"做靚條數only"},{"pid":"48ce3c38bf4d5d84cb7a2545ce5f65558b4164fd","tid":2123183,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"休班賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70145de7deb5617f3f7f2fc69401913fd0c940d","tid":2123183,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"